[*] --> Delivered
Delivered --> Shipped : submit
Shipped --> Approved : process
Approved --> Draft : update
Draft --> Closed : update
Draft : entry / log classroom
Closed --> Rejected : cancel
Closed : entry / log classroom
Rejected --> Draft : revert
Rejected --> [*]
